{"lemma":"حَفَناتُ","slug":"حَفَناتُ","root":"ح.ف.ن","root_slug":"ح-ف-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ف-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8531","n8534","n8535"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%8E%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8531","headword_ar":"حَفَنَهُ","root":"Hfn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (PS, TK,) [or"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in a phrase following,] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafonN","text_ar":"حَفْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the palms of his two hands and with the fingers put together"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to make the two hands like a bowl"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he scooped it up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"out,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarafahu","text_ar":"جَرَفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with both his hands:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) said only of what is dry, as flour, and sand, and the like. (S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hafana Alqawoma","text_ar":"حَفَنَ القَوْمَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave to every one of the party a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hafonap","text_ar":"حَفْنَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hafana lahu","text_ar":"حَفَنَ لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hafana lahu HafonapF","text_ar":"حَفَنَ لَهُ حَفْنَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafonN","text_ar":"حَفْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave to him a small quantity."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hafana AlmaA='a EalaY raA^osihi","text_ar":"حَفَنَ المَا=ءَ عَلَى رَاْسِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He threw the water upon his head with his two hands"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put together so as to be like a bowl"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IAar, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","PS","TK","M","K","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n8534","headword_ar":"حَفْنَةٌ","root":"Hfn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, TA, and so, accord. to the TA, in the K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HufonapN","text_ar":"حُفْنَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in copies of the K,) [but the former is that which is commonly known,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A handful:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quantity that fills the two hands"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when they are put together so as to be like a bowl"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, Msb;) of wheat [or the like]: (S:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafanaAtN","text_ar":"حَفَنَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb.) Hence, (in the saying of Aboo-Bekr, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~amaA","text_ar":"اـِنَّمَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHonu HafonapN mino HafanaAti A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"نَحْنُ حَفْنَةٌ مِنْ حَفَنَاتِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) i. e., (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We shall be but little,"},{"kind":"text","text":"on the day of resurrection,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hfnp","text_ar":"حفنة"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the estimation"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of God;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) meaning we shall be but a small thing in comparison with the dominion and the mercy of God. (S, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaf~","text_ar":"كَفّ"},{"kind":"text","text":") itself. (Har p. 296.) ―         -b3-  See also what next follows."}],"source_refs":["Mgh","K","S","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n8535","headword_ar":"حُفْنَةٌ","root":"Hfn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hollow, cavity, trench,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, dug,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excavated, in the ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wherever it be;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excavated by a torrent in rugged ground, in the channel of the water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hollow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cavity, in the ground, such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuqorap","text_ar":"نُقْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISk, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having in it water, and in its bottom pebbles and earth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafonapN","text_ar":"حَفْنَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a well,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL:) pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HufanN","text_ar":"حُفَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) which is explained by Sh as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small round hollows"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cavities, in which rain-water stagnates, excavated by the water, in the form of pools."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafonapN","text_ar":"حَفْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","ISk","KL"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}